    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This A80 Supra features the iconic 2JZ-GTE sequential twin-turbocharged inline-six, delivering linear power through the bulletproof Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its rigidity with a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension setup and a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise cornering exit. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and refreshing of the vacuum lines for the sequential actuators. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, offering the raw, mechanical engagement that defined the 90s JDM era.",
